    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK977">
<l>iṟappē purinta toḻiṟṟāñ ciṟappuntāṉ</l>
<l>cīral lavarkaṭ paṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even nobility of birth, wealth and learning, if in (the possession of) the base, will (only) produce everincreasing pride.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
